! Modified Colemak layout.
!
!   - Swaps Y and J (see http://www.mntnoe.com/2008/09/danish-vim-friendy-colemak-layout)
!   - Qwerty P = Backspace (easier to hit -- backspace is one of the most hit keys on the keyboard)
!   - Caps Lock = Escape
!   - AltGr = Right Alt (more ergonomic)
!   - Shift has moved a step to the right as shift on the european keyboard is smaller.
!   - The original shift acts as AltGr and is used for window management bindings and danish characters.


clear Control
clear Lock
clear Mod1
clear Mod2
clear Mod3
clear Mod4
clear Mod5
clear Shift

